Caroline Oudo is 17 years old but in form two. She has been suffering from skin disease since she completed standard eight and is also having great problems with her eyes. She is an orphan with six other siblings. Despite all her problems Caroline works hard and performs well She is very determined to excel  and all she needs is a good sympathiser and well wisher who can assist her to complete her education. She lives in a small house 10' x 10', two kilometers from school.
